reviewText: My grandson loved the muppet tape,HE IS A 22YR OLD WITH DOWNSYNDROME. He will only watcha few tapes  and muppets is his favorite, You were fast with delivery,It was in good shape,and i`m very happy with the order,  Thank you,  Judy k.

This is a collector's dream!  We love this video.  Unfortunately the quality of this used video was not what the seller had said.  There was some audio and video problems.  But we just love Kermie and Miss Piggy and this is a video kids of ALL AGES should have.  The humor is more for the adults - but all kids love it!  Recommend the video to everyone!
